snippet.title: Zero Reflex - Launch trailer
snippet.description:
Circles, bullets, shurikens, rockets, saws and time ... they're all after you!

Zero Reflex is a psychedelic evader which tests both your dexterity and your nerves in a fast-paced punishing environment that keeps pushing your limits.

Zero Reflex puts 80 challenges in front of you.

You have no save points and no excuses! Be faster than a blink of the Eye!

Steam - PC, Linux, & Mac
http://store.steampowered.com/app/405650/

App Store – iOS
http://itunes.apple.com/us/app/zero-reflex/id1003727635 

Google Play – Android 
http://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.exordium.eyewillsurvivelite
